title: Leaf Shape Dog Blanket
description:
Leaf shape blanket with a soft touch, let your pup lying on it or tuck them in this softness, enjoy a lazy cozy afternoon.

These cute colors and design also give your home a nice decor.

Dual usages, as a mat or a blanket
Machine Washable, stay in shape
100% cotton, soft touch
Big size for big pup

title: Dog Bed Car Seat
description:
Move your dog's bed in the car! This dog bed can be used as a seat cover, protect your car seat and keep it clean, which makes your dog more comfortable on the road.

 
Dog bed for car
Durable
Protect car seat
Soft-touch with the pillow on the edge
Anti-slip
Waterproof
Easy to install
Machine washable
